name: Bali Countryside Sidemen
address: Jalan Raya Satria Sidemen Banjar Kebon Desa Sukahet, FCRG+XF3, Lokasari, Kec. Sidemen, Kabupaten Karangasem, Bali 80864, Indonesia
review 1: Real Bali is in the countryside. Sideman is a classic example. It's beautiful, clean and fresh. Strongly recommend people visiting Bali to spend a couple of days here
review 2: Fantastic tour! Tommy the guide was awesome!
review 4: The view of sidemen village is awesome, fresh air and so clear
review 5: Nice vibe's, green site, my opinion this is great place for pre wedding photos, and even wedding celebration if you love nature stuff , they have good views , rice fields, hills , and Agung Vulcano is tottaly shown from this site on a bright day, bamboo paviliun and local fruits are growing arround the area and garden, love this place!!,  üëçüëçüëç
